<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Harbinger started as buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Harbinger started as buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- First Albany Corp said it initiated coverage of Harbinger Corp as a buy.</p>
<p>-- said Harbinger has consistently beat Wall Street earnings estimates.</p>
<p>-- said the company's revenue and earnings growth exceeds that of its peers.</p>
<p>-- said Harbinger has demonstrated skill at making key strategic acquisitions and integrating them.</p>
<p>-- set a 12-month price target of $36 a share.</p>
<p>-- Harbinger was off 1/8 to 23-5/8.</p>
<p>((--Wall Street Desk 212-859-1730))</p>
